，用廣東話</blockquote><br />\n唔通用普通話咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de17a4c3fd931521c8aae203b5ad43b0fb846786","tid":29187,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係財務公司都係中介嘅一種<br />\n咪畀錢中介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n此中介不同彼中介。<br />\n嗰啲中介口頭上會話幫你去某財務公司申請借貸，但係實上無幫你借到錢，仲攞你嘅資料去做其他用途，總之最後你唔單止借唔到錢之餘，佢哋仲會畀重債你還。年中唔少人都係因為咁而自殺。"},{"pid":"9a5abc2ad686f11072a8d4bdeb3b00880a408ac8","tid":29187,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"用返牛熊窩輪果句，貸款受條款約束，即 terms and conditons apply仲好，簡單易明"}]}